Detailed Description

Symbolic constants for common atoms.

The following atoms have symbolic constants: t, nil, quote, ., atom, eq, car, cdr, cons, cond, lambda and label. Strictly speaking, dot (.) is not an atom. However, the parser treats it as one while scanning the text before it filters it out.
